<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ف ظ ظ:</span> <span class="c2">(الْفَظُّ)</span> مِنَ الرِّجَالِ الْغَلِيظُ وَقَدْ <span class="c2">(فَظَّ)</span> يَفَظُّ بِالْفَتْحِ <span class="c2">(فَظَاظَةً)</span> بِفَتْحِ الْفَاءِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>